solution: ```class Solution {
    public int sumOfTheDigitsOfHarshadNumber(int x) {
        if (x == 0) return -1;
        int n = x, sum = 0;
        while (n != 0) {
            sum += n % 10;
            n /= 10;
        }
        return (x % sum == 0) ? sum : -1;
    }
}
```
